type: software
title: "Context Bazaar & Kanon "
abstract: "Kanon is a CLI tool for authoring knowledge artifacts (skills, powers, rules, workflows, prompts, agents, templates, reference packs) in a single canonical format and compiling them to any supported AI coding assistant harness, including Kiro, Claude Code, GitHub Copilot, Cursor, Windsurf, Cline, and Amazon Q Developer. Context Bazaar is the accompanying catalog of artifacts."
version: 0.5.0
date-released: "2026-07-08"
license: MIT
